---

---

<section id="about" class="relative py-20 md:py-28 bg-surface-alt">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Section header -->
    <div class="mb-16 reveal">
      <span class="font-mono text-xs text-accent uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4 block">About</span>
      <h2 class="text-[clamp(2rem,4vw,3.5rem)] font-display font-bold text-heading">
        Who Is Behind the Data
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Photo area -->
      <div class="relative reveal">
        <div class="aspect-[3/4] rounded-2xl bg-surface border border-border overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center shadow-[0_1px_3px_rgba(0,0,0,0.04)]">
          <div class="text-center p-8">
            <!-- Gradient ring avatar -->
            <div class="relative w-40 h-40 mx-auto mb-6">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-accent via-blue to-amber animate-[spin_8s_linear_infinite] opacity-70"></div>
              <div class="absolute inset-[3px] rounded-full bg-surface flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="font-display text-5xl font-bold text-gradient">AR</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-muted font-mono">Photo coming soon</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Decorative accent -->
        <div class="absolute -bottom-3 -right-3 w-24 h-24 border border-accent/20 rounded-2xl -z-10"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Bio -->
      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-heading mb-2">
          Artem Reiter
        </h3>
        <span class="font-mono text-sm text-accent mb-6 block">Founder & Lead Analyst</span>

        <div class="space-y-4 text-body leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            I've spent 8+ years turning messy analytics into clear business intelligence.
            From startups burning ad budgets on broken tracking to enterprises drowning in
            dashboards nobody reads — I've seen it all and fixed it.
          </p>
          <p class="text-heading/80 italic border-l-2 border-accent/30 pl-4">
            "My approach is simple: your analytics should answer business questions, not create
            new ones. Every tag, every event, every dashboard exists for a reason — or it doesn't exist."
          </p>
          <p>
            Before founding Reiterweb, I led analytics at several product companies and consulted
            for agencies across Europe. I'm Google Analytics certified, BigQuery proficient, and
            unreasonably passionate about clean data layers.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Credentials -->
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          {['Google Analytics Certified', 'BigQuery', 'GTM Expert', '50+ Projects'].map((badge) => (
            <span class="text-xs font-mono text-muted px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-border bg-surface">
              {badge}
            </span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
